<h5 class="updated-marker highlight"><span class="time"><a href="#protesters-block-interstate-44-in-st-louis">12:42 A.M.</a></span><strong>Protesters Block Interstate 44 in St. Louis </strong></h5>
</div>
<div class="updated-entry-content">
<div class="w480">
<figure class="media photo promo" itemprop="" itemscope="" itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/11/26/us/FERGUSONBLOG-INTERSTATE/FERGUSONBLOG-INTERSTATE-blog480.jpg" itemtype="//schema.org/ImageObject" role="group"><span class="visually-hidden">Photo</span>
<div class="image"><img itemprop="url" itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/11/26/us/FERGUSONBLOG-INTERSTATE/FERGUSONBLOG-INTERSTATE-blog480.jpg" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/11/26/us/FERGUSONBLOG-INTERSTATE/FERGUSONBLOG-INTERSTATE-blog480.jpg" id="100000003254220" width="480" height="291" alt="Protesters shut down Interstate 44Â at Grand Avenue in both directions in St. Louis on Monday."   /><meta itemprop="height" content="291"><meta itemprop="width" content="480"></div>
<figcaption class="caption" itemprop="description"><span class="caption-text">Protesters shut down Interstate 44Â at Grand Avenue in both directions in St. Louis on Monday.</span><span class="credit" itemprop="copyrightHolder"><span class="visually-hidden">Credit</span> J.B. Forbes/St. Louis Post-Dispatch, via Associated Press</span></figcaption>
</figure>
