<div class="type-live-update update">
<div id="flight-restrictions-at-lambert-st-louis-international" class="updated-entry">
<h5 class="updated-marker highlight"><span class="time"><a href="#flight-restrictions-at-lambert-st-louis-international">12:29 A.M.</a></span><strong>Flight restrictions at Lambert-St. Louis International </strong></h5>
</div>
<div class="updated-entry-content">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Inbound flights to Lambert-St. Louis International Airport were not being permitted to land late Monday as a safety precaution, officials said. The Federal Aviation Administration issued a temporary flight restriction, or TFR, affecting inbound flights, the airport said<a href="https://www.twitter.com/flystl/status/537106706791415809"> in a post on Twitter</a>. </p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">&#8212; <em>EMMA FITZSIMMONS</em></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="type-live-update update">
