</figure>
</div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Mayor James Knowles III of Ferguson, reached on his cellphone late Monday, said he was in Ferguson and wanted to see National Guard troops moving in to protect his city.<br />
&#8220;Theyâre here in the area. I donât know why they&#8217;re not deploying,&#8221; said Mr. Knowles, who declined to comment further because of the continuing emergency.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">&#8212; <em>MITCHELL SMITH</em></p>
</div>
