<div id="police-say-ferguson-protests-turn-dangerous" class="updated-entry">
<h5 class="updated-marker highlight"><span class="time"><a href="#police-say-ferguson-protests-turn-dangerous">11:51 P.M.</a></span><strong> Police Say Ferguson Protests Turn Dangerous</strong></h5>
</div>
<div class="updated-entry-content">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Protests in Ferguson became dangerous on Monday night, with two police cars set on fire and reports of looting at stores and gunfire, the police said.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">The St. Louis County police posted updates on the protests to Twitter throughout the night. Officers used pepper spray and smoke in an effort to disperse the crowd, the police said.</p>
