<h5 class="updated-marker highlight"><span class="time"><a href="#transcripts-of-the-grand-jury-proceedings-2">11:33 P.M.</a></span><strong>Transcript of the Grand Jury Proceedings</strong></h5>
</div>
<div class="updated-entry-content">
