<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">The documents were released by the St. Louis County prosecutor, Robert P. McCulloch.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">&#8212; <em>THE NEW YORK TIMES</em></p>
