<h5 class="updated-marker highlight"><span class="time"><a href="#gov-jay-nixon-calls-for-peace-2">6:51 P.M.</a></span><strong>Gov. Jay Nixon Calls for Peace</strong></h5>
</div>
<div class="updated-entry-content">
<div class="w480"><figure class="promo media video blog-video "
